      <title>债券市场的兴奋转向美联储需要降到多低的争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/treasury-bond-euphoria-shifts-to-market-debate-on-fed-rate-cut-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券市场的强劲反弹表明交易员相信美联储的加息周期已经结束。现在的争论转向央行行长何时开始降息以及降息幅度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/treasury-bond-euphoria-shifts-to-market-debate-on-fed-rate-cut-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着全球价格压力减弱，澳大利亚将采取鹰派立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/australia-set-for-hawkish-hold-as-global-price-pressures-abate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行将恢复暂停加息，因为最新数据显示房价增长放缓，而通胀表明之前的紧缩举措正在获得牵引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/australia-set-for-hawkish-hold-as-global-price-pressures-abate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
